reviewText: cute, My grand-daughter is interested in face painting and makeup this was nice to see and gave me ideas for her Christmas present this year.

This only shows you one design and it's of the young girl on the front.  Other designs are shown as completed, but there is no step-by-step illustration.  I found this very disappointing considering the cost.  You can find much better stuff on YouTube and it's free.

I didn't mean to watch this video all the way through but I did. I don't do face painting but decided to take a peak at this video anyway. What a gem. The teaching was clear and the camera was right where it should be. There was a nice little surprise at the end with many inspirational ideas. Even though I don't face paint for a living, I'd do this at a birthday party for sure. Thanks!
For anyone with kids... --- this video is AMAZING.....  Def. Worth it!!! - Your Kids and Your Family will love it!
